Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於小時候發過高燒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的右耳有些失聰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她基本上都走在我的左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是默契的特等席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上回跟葉月君午飯一起吃拉麵已經是一星期前的事了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道這算不算久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說了那種話之後卻什麼也沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊這算是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人問待宵草和月見草是不是同一種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是同一種哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵很相似所以很容易混淆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要哪種呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待宵草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用這個花為基調做一小束花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用待宵草就可以了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是它的花語是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見異思遷 反覆無常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣合適麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君也是待宵草麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這個搬到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 店長的生日就花在和美惠小姐輪班看店上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我那膚淺的智慧完全想不出來店長喜歡什麼禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店裡下班後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只好用那天發的工資買了一盆巨大的蔓綠絨回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能想到買東西為店裡做點貢獻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實要是知道店長喜歡什麼的話讓我做什麼都行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君啊 你超級膽小吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是誰阻礙了我的去路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣子你真夠差勁的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人火大啊你這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和店長一說話你就肯定會使的那招算啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼臉表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心讓人笑不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你貌似跟店長還說過不少大方話來著吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上不就是個超級粘人的嘮叨丈夫麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也說的太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很平常的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡啊 結果做得最差勁的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我想往店長那邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的後腦勺就會淡定地出現在我眼前就這樣循環往復
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不被你整得鬥志全無麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在不覺得自己有礙著你個弄哭自家老婆的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 人生路不可能一帆風順的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說這種話很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說很現實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到現在我才會去想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開的一方和被留下的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得到底哪個更痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我把一生的眼淚都流乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方一片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混亂得不知道從何下手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個人也沒在我守靈的時候起死回生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只是一副白骨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我被忙碌拯救活到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君 我記得他好像很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去也很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學不乖的男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 今天下班後要不要一起吃個飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說吃飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不看我 是害羞了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將店長帶出去她就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子說的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮過了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很認真地考慮過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君你才是 真的有好好考慮過麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可是結過婚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選我能有什麼好處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能只憑這種利益關係來決定是不是就會輕鬆不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會輕鬆不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 和我交往的話你能得不少好處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道會是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在小六花的右邊的人 明明應該是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在居然是這種站位 真不像樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和最喜歡的女生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 你別走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 留在我身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別留下我一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人生的結尾處跟你兩個人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你那時候讓我留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才會決定 哪兒也不去了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃 芝士好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼餡的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是大蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴大概很臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 右肩感覺有點癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣和男生並排坐在一起 真是久違了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太辣了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是辣椒油的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家店的東西真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這店很出名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜誌上還有介紹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早以前就知道這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是再這樣發呆下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會哪天就和葉月君睡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是嚴禁事項
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到上周為止還以為戀愛什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經一輩子都和自己無緣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 有點臉紅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很臭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等…等…請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要是跟來的話就跟你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝點水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送快遞的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是您的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請蓋個章
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那個…簽名也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說了跟來就絕交的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不管怎麼樣應該都不會絕交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我剛才那麼丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的 你做這種事我可是會想歪的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我本來就有那種打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還輕易讓我進來我可是會抱有幻想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我從一開始就有那種打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有大蒜的臭味 我也不會退縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長居然把眼睛閉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊兒去啊 臭怨靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣了啊 太不像樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於說出心裡話了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對讓你忘乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的老公什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 本來是對這傢伙說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼嚴肅地皺著眉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我說…我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用那麼順便一說的語氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一把年紀了 還這麼搖擺不定的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真是丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生平第一次對別人起了殺心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對方本來就不是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓小六花幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然比我小八歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟會做這麼可愛的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就被他帶著走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能 很久違了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花居然會歎氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住院後 她就沒露出過疲勞的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店裡的事情沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君你出院前美惠姐她們也會來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才醫生過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是果然 還是不能生小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟以前做過放射線治療
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然原因也不止這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(262,169)\frz343.2}離婚協議書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜託姐姐給我拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經蓋好章了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在這個樣子 也沒必要講究什麼形式了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一看到這東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 在這世上最喜歡的就是島尾君你的插花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在職校時第一次看到你作品時的那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到現在還我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來「要讓花鮮活得有花的樣子」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的就是這麼回事啊 我當時這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那些修剪過頭顯得太假的插花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或那些稀奇古怪只想引人注目的插花不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所追求的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連花兒凋零或枯萎時的美也一併肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安寧時或放棄時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜悅 悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富有 或貧窮時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看你老婆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你活著我就很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣在這裡睡著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說小六花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 身體上到處都使不上勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…這可不是什麼好兆頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了要你蓋著被子睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻連幫她蓋上一條毛毯都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到開店時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不先拜託誰幫我看下店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還能開車麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣不能開車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是剛吃了退燒藥麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了 頭好暈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…我得去洗個澡才成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你想病情惡化麼笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先…發個短信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不爽啊 怎麼感覺聽到那只冤鬼的叫聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是叫的店長的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美惠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花有沒有給你發短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到的短信內容很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到的是個空短信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來英雄救美的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉 一大早就被冤鬼盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說廢話快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙放在後門那從裡面數過來第二盆姬朧月的花盆下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那盆茶色的多肉植物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說只有我能看到這個幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是按他的指示這樣進去的話應該算是非法入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 島尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臥室就在那裡 你前面那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥放在電話旁的籃子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是冷敷貼用完了還有凍著的冰塊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才她已經喝過補充維他命的飲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心店裡的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還有存貨 美惠小姐會按時過來開店的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾…君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要哭的人 是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:31.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも夢の中では あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:31.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢中的你永遠是笑著的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:38.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしてね 消えないの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:38.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不會消失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.76,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I care you everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.76,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關心你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You care me everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你關心我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:46.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっといつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:46.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是永久的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still my everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛してるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:59.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏に降った 雪のような
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:59.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正如盛夏裡飄落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:04.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:04.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個易碎的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:06.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:06.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我為何是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:11.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:11.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是沒有遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:18.69,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんなに切なくて 胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:18.69,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也不會如此絞痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:22.61,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こともなかったそれでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:22.61,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:28.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会えなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:28.30,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是沒能遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:35.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強さも優しさも 知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:35.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就無法領悟強大與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:44.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目を閉じればすぐそこに あなたがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:44.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼你就在離我那麼近的地方

